[11]Culture and utilisationsIl has been planted for commercial purposes for the paper industry at different latitudes and altitudes in different parts of the world : in the equatorial regions and tropical as in Kenya, Tanzania, Angola, but also in temperate regions of the subtropics, as in the hightlands of South Africa, in higher altitudes in the south of Brazil, in the north of India, also in temperate regions at medium altitudes and low in the provinces in argentina, Salta, Tucuman and Cordoba ; between 500 m and 1500 m altitude.
